name: Anllela Sagra
description:
A request of @gw2herb in my buymeacoffee website.

Anllela Sagra is a Colombian fitness model and social media celebrity.

Really sorry for the quick update, guys. Should have checked step 500 before I uploaded the previous one! Please check the "About this version" section for more info.

Remember that, in case you encounter saturation, you can reduce the embedding weight. For instance, type "(anllesagra:0.98)" in your prompt.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)
